# Assumptions

# Current Floor is at 0 or ground floor
# Building has 6 floors total ( -2 -1 0 1 2 3), Negative numbers represent basement floors and positive numbers are floors above ground level
# Top Floor defined as floor 3, bottom floor defined as -2
